description.value: On a critical hit, the creature is restrained instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.
On a critical hit, the creature is restrained instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.
If the Bone Prancer moved over 10 feet before attacking, it deals an additional [[/r 2d8 #damage]]{2d8 damage}.

The prancer is incapacitated while in the area of an antimagic field. If targeted by the Dispel Magic spell, the prancer must succeed on a Fortitude saving throw against the caster's spell save DC or fall @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Unconscious]{Unconscious} for 1 minute.
On a critical hit, the creature is restrained instead. The Bone Prancer may only restrain one creature in this manner.

The Bone Prancer may stride up to its speed. If it has a creature @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Restrained]{Restrained}, it may move them with itself. The restrained creatures suffers [[/r 2d6[bludgeoning]]] damage for every 10 feet moved in this manner.
